kid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And that is a goat, that's been chilling,\\\" Bacon said in avideo shared to XonAug.\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2as he moved a glass with a goat figurine perched on the rim in the camera frame.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The cocktail, which appeared to be a spicy margarita measured from the heart, was mixed with tequila, chili powder (because Biles \\\"is fire\\\"), a dash of maple syrup, and of course, plenty of lime.\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end, he shared the drink's name - the \\\"iced out GOAT.\\\"\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"score\": 0.7168567345960191, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GOAT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The name is likely a reference toBiles' new blingthat she debuted after winning her second gold medal in Paris, and ninth Olympic medal overall, in the all-around competition Aug. 1.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999816054699, \"rank\": 1.839444981493431e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cementing her status as one of the greatest gymnasts of all time, she wore a custom-made necklace with a diamond-encrusted goat figure - a symbol that plays up the abbreviation for greatest of all time, or GOAT.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"score\": 0.7168567345960191, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GOAT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Captioning his recipe video, Bacon wrote, \\\"A drink fit for a GOAT.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Congrats @Simone_Biles and the entire women's gymnastics team!\\\"\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bacon is one of many celebrities, whether it be in Paris or at home, that were cheering on the U.S. women's gymnastics team.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999816054699, \"rank\": 1.839444981493431e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Law & Order: SVU\\\" starMariska Hargitay met a shocked Jordan Chiles and Suni Leeat the Olympics Aug. 2.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dragunov_SVU\", \"score\": 0.9999842824907438, \"rank\": 1.4220193078445472e-05, \"text\": \"SVU\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dragunov_SVU\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dragunov_SVU\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The actor and gymnasts also chatted with the king of viral Olympic moments,Snoop Dogg.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Celebrities and athletes, including Kendall Jenner, Martha Stewart, Seth Rogen, Serena Williams and more, were also in attendance for the all-around competition,per Olympics.com.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1580, \"end\": 1594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kendall_Jenner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"